data.description: ASSUMABLE LOAN WITH LOW INTREST RATE & SELLER CREDIT OFFERED! With a strong offer sellers is offering up to $10,000 credit at closing for paint and flooring, closing cost, or rate buy down. Buyers choice. Current loan possible to assume by qualified buyer. Now is your chance to own this single level home in the beautiful Lakeview Estate community with-in the Oakland School District. Open concept kitchen and living space with vaulted ceilings. The large primary bedroom features an ensuite and walk-in closet, and opens to a private back patio. Large corner lot with RV parking and a wraparound porch.
